  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] actually, it was-- they were talking about it, that it's going to be formed before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody prepared themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't have enough-- enough space to put all of those people because they wanted to put in a small part of Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took the-- the worst-- where the poor people were living mostly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before they formed the ghetto, they made the first action.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- they announced that able-bodied man had to come and register to come in the morning and be-- whoever didn't work, who didn't-- whoever didn't-- because I was working, for instance, for the-- for my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was not necessary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was not something that I could show that I'm working because it was not considered worthwhile work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they were talking that there are going to be ghettos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somehow, people had some kind of a connection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody-- a rumor started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's going to be an action.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A ghetto in Krakow was already in place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So and-- so-- I remember I didn't have a-- a working place-- a working stamp, a real good working stamp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they-- and my-- and my-- everybody was trying to find out because they were getting [INAUDIBLE] cards at that time, an official thing that you are really working.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister started-- we had a cousin who was working as-- in the-- in the-- it was established, a police, sort of a Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were watching the-- the people, how-- like they have to tell people not to walk on the sidewalk or not to walk here, not to walk there, and-- small things.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
